ber generator, is that a Hold or a Sell? I think it=E2=80=99s a Hold, right=
? It would be insane to *short* that, anyway.[2] Or here=E2=80=99s a questi=
on that seems practical but still has a meme-stock tinge: =E2=80=9CWould yo=
u consider selling AMC merchandise at theaters and on online platforms, I t=
hink it will be profitable.=E2=80=9D I feel like two years ago no one would=
 have thought to buy *AMC* merch: If you love movies, you might buy merch f=
or specific movies, maybe even for a studio, but for a movie-theater chain?=
 Now of course AMC is a beloved brand, but realistically if you=E2=80=99re =
buying AMC merch (1) it=E2=80=99s because you like the stock and (2) it wil=
l have a gorilla on it.[3] =E2=80=9COne question,=E2=80=9D on an earnings c=
